channel.description: idk but moparscape has a very good status page but i prefer runelocus' toplist. If someone knows how they make these auto voters lemme no cuz on their site you can only vote once every 24 hrs. It's kinda weird i just wanna chat about how they got around it.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 29, 2009, 09:33:38 pm[/size][hr]lmao they already blanked out the name to google but most people knwo where im talking about
